<h2>What is Tefter?</h2>

<p>
Tefter (notebook) is a web based <em>free</em> application for personal expense tracking.
The features are loosely based on the methodology described in <a href="http://www.yourmoneyoryourlife.org/">Your Money or Your Life</a>.
</p>

<h2>Claim Back Your Life</h2>

<p>Originally, my main purpose was to figure out where do I spend my money (scratching my own itch).
The process was painful and elightening as time passed.</p>

<p>
At certain point, the stats gathered allowed me to make predictions on my financial state in a given period.
</p>

